snippet.title: Hide Time: Chapter 1 - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/hidetime/761589
Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2143180/Hide_Time/?beta=0  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
You are a detective who is sent by the police to find some missing children in a toy store! You stay stuck in the building and try to find a new way out!  By:  @SirGx3  and  @Oski29 ​
